items.title: Satyayoddha Kalki 1
items.description: After a defeat at the hands of Lord Kali, Kalki Hari must journey towards the Mahendragiri mountains with his companions to finally become the avatar he is destined to be. But the road ahead is not without peril . . .
items.author: Kevin Missal
